channel.title: Half a Web Client! [Half Working :/]
channel.description:
[url=http://www.zyroxic.com/weird.htm]HERE or IS IT HERE[/url]. BUT this is only half working since it only loads some of the cache (Hard to explain) before i can finish it I need some help..... Alright which class loads the animations and models???? I'm sure at least one of you know where... I will make a tut on how to make this thingy when I finish but for now I kinda need help...
P.S: This doesnt use Jaggrab :), It is very decompilable so if your looking for the loading method thing its in "method132"...
~Have fun this is probably gonna be the most working web client you'll see for like a while so thats why im posting....
